Thank you for coming agent.
We seem to have a situation here.

There has been a bomb threat and
we have a reason to believe it is genuine.

Given you are the only agent in the
area, we had no choice.

You must save the school from destruction.
We've sent you this as soon as we 
received intel on the bomb.

The location is yet unknown,
but if you are listening to this 
immediately after receiving it, you 
should have 20 minutes until it detonates.

You will need to find your own equipment 
for bomb diffusal as there was 
no time to send you any.

This is your last chance Agent.

If you fail this assignment,
you better hope the explosion 
takes you with it because if it 
doesn't take you out, we will.

This tape will self destruct in 10 seconds.
Please remove tape and toss it away now.